<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br>I’m following up on my previous attempts to provide you with a quote for your business insurance.&nbsp;<br><br>I understand that there can be many reasons why you may not be interested right now and I wanted to check if any of these apply to you.<br><font size="4"><b><br>Current policy not due to expire?<br></b></font>If you let me know your expiry date for your business insurance policy, I can give you a call nearer the time to arrange your quote.<br><b><font size="4"><br>Got a quote elsewhere?<br></font></b>We can often match like-for-like quotes, so if you let us know the cover levels and the quoted price you have received I can see if we can provide a better quote for you.<br><font size="4"><b><br>Want no further contact?<br></b></font>If you are not interested in receiving a quote, just let me know and I will ensure I don’t contact you again.&nbsp;<br><br>Alternatively, if you are still interested in proceeding with your quote&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href="https://calendly.com/d/cm3g-k74-js2/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>book a call with me</b></a>,&nbsp;let me know the best date and time for me to call you or give me a ring&nbsp;on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.&nbsp;<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>